{"tid":275984,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"Gwent: The Witcher Card Game - Open Beta [2]","createTime":"2017-06-08T12:39:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-10T05:12:20.000Z","uid":47247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"da6c887a2ffe44732e4e97252e0f5f548794ede7","tid":275984,"uid":47247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T12:39:10.000Z","msg":"昆特牌係內自巫師系列的一個遊戲,再引伸一個獨立遊戲<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.playgwent.com/en\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.playgwent.com%2Fen&d=cDpCooU48CyrVJafXT1IoghMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=0baaf9f8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.playgwent.com/en</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n基本玩法<br />\n<br />\n雙方都有分數,鬥分數最大者為勝<br />\n三場兩勝制.有和波情況<br />\n<br />\n流程.<br />\n<br />\n大家抽10張牌,大家可以開始前換三張牌<br />\n遊戲就正式開始<br />\n<br />\n先攻為隨機(舊時版本綠卡Scoiatael可以自由選擇,而家公測無左.)<br />\n<br />\n每局結算後將場上所有卡送墓<br />\n第二回合開始<br />\n<br />\n第二回合開始既時候雙方再抽2張牌.再換1張牌.<br />\n第三回合開始既時候雙方只可抽1張牌.再換1張牌<br />\n<br />\n常用連結:<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.gwentdb.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gwentdb.com%2F&d=cDpCooU48CyrVJafXT1IoghMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=5b856d59\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.gwentdb.com/</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://gwentify.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgwentify.com%2F&d=cDpCooU48CyrVJafXT1IoghMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=052cbc68\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://gwentify.com/</a><br />\n<br />\n方便各位netdeck <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24d74392e593d13d2101f9cc2450eb0e4e5a6793","tid":275984,"uid":28868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T05:12:20.000Z","msg":"仲有冇人玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}